ion\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span> <span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>file<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">image</code> 선택을 할때 비디오 영상인 아닌 image만 선택하기 위해서 <code class=\"language-text\">accept=\"image/*</code>를 사용했다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"appjs\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#appjs\" aria-label=\"appjs permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>app.js</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> file <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"file\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">onFileSelect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> file <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>files<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> url <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token constant\">URL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createObjectURL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>file<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//file을 가리키는 url을 DOMstring으로 반환합니다. </span>\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> image <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Image</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//image 객체를 생성해 속성들을 추가할 수 있음</span>\r\n  image<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>src <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> url<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//image 속성 </span>\r\n  image<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onload</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">drawImage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">800</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">800</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n  file<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n  \r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"onfileselect-함수\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#onfileselect-%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98\" aria-label=\"onfileselect 함수 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>onFileSelect() 함수</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">const url = URL.createObjectURL(file)</code> <code class=\"language-text\">files</code>을 가리키는 <code class=\"language-text\">url</code> 을 <code class=\"language-text\">DOMstring</code> 으로 반환한다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">const image = new Image()</code> image 객체를 생성해 속성들을 추가할 수 있다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">image.onload</code> 함수 내의 명령은 웹브라우저 내의 모든 요소가 준비된 후 실행이 되도록 힌다..</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">image</code> 라는 객체가 이미지를 불러온 후에 함수를 실행한다.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#html\">Html</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"date":"March 30, 2023","title":"Canvas (4)","categories":"Canvas Js","author":"Js","emoji":"🖋"},"fields":{"slug":"/Canvas/Canvas(4)/"}},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://www.zoomkoding.com","comments":{"utterances":{"repo":"dony0720/dony0720.github.io"}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Canvas/Canvas(3)/","nextSlug":"/Git/git2/","prevSlug":"/Canvas/Canvas(4)/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1073350324","1956554647","2938748437"]}